BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:★★ VIX最終決済
DTSTART:20260519T123000Z
DTEND:20260519T123500Z
DTSTAMP:20260503T080405Z
UID:5886fd97bb227dd1@us-market-cal
CATEGORIES:opex
DESCRIPTION:VIX Final Settlement (AM settlement)\nET 08:30 / JST 21:30\n
 出典: CBOE (vix_exceptions.csv)\nSOQ (Special Opening Quotation) で決
 済値算出 | 不規則（火曜）Juneteenth 6/19でSPX 6月限が6/18
 木に繰上→30日前逆算
